# RunAgents Agent — {{name}}

This project is a RunAgents AI agent. Key patterns:

- Agent code lives in `agent.py` with a `handler(request, ctx)` function
- Configuration in `runagents.yaml` (tools, model, system prompt)
- Use `from runagents import Agent` for the SDK
- `agent.call_tool(name, path, payload)` to call platform tools
- `agent.chat(message, tools=...)` for LLM completions
- Local dev: `runagents dev` (starts on :8080)
- Deploy: `runagents deploy`

Tools are external APIs registered on the platform. The mesh handles auth.
Do not hardcode API keys or manage OAuth tokens in agent code.
